content: There are Homeplus and Daiso restaurants in the basement, so it's easy to shop for food, and on the other ground floor, there are various shopping streets and theaters, including maker clothing stores.
An nice place to unwind, window shopping  and others..wonderful place to go.
Shopping is also shopping, but there are many restaurants, so I often go to dinner!
It's always nice to have a Christmas tree in winter! It's nice to have an arcade!
It was a picnic for my children. It was so good. Especially.. There is also a library, so it is very necessary. You can also take a walk in the backyard.
It's good to go with children. The disadvantage is that you have to go to Gangseo-gu to find a restaurant.
